#

Savory Pork Gravy Over Creamy Polenta with Sautéed Green Beans

$15.99
620 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Comfort FoodAmerican CuisineHearty Meal

Description

A rich and savory pork gravy served over smooth, creamy polenta, complemented by tender sautéed green beans for a delightful balance of flavors and textures.

Ingredients

  • Pork shoulder: 1 lb
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Onion: 1 large, diced
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Chicken broth: 2 cups
  • Soy sauce: 2 tbsp
  • Cornstarch: 2 tbsp
  • Milk: 1 cup
  • Polenta: 1 cup
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Green beans: 1 lb, trimmed
  • Butter: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
